Dialogue: 100,0:00:05.42,0:00:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dacă eroii, care au salvat lumea, \Nși-ar fi putut găsi liniștea,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}misiunea lor ar fi luat sfârșit.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.13,0:00:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dar aceștia au fost denunțați și condamnați la moarte de către cei pe care-i salvaseră.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.93,0:00:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oamenii au spus că nu \Nmai aveau nevoie de ei.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.95,0:00:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dar asta este nedrept.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.83,0:01:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eroii, care au săvârșit fapte legendare,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.87,0:01:40.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nu ar trebui să aibă parte \Nde o moarte așa de crudă.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dacă mureau când încă erau eroi,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.76,0:01:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aceștia revenuau la viață \Ndrept cetățeni obișnuiți.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.57,0:01:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reintegrarea eroilor în societate,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:50.18,0:01:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}asta este treaba Agenției de Pensioare și Reacomodare a Eroilor.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eroine gemene?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.19,0:02:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:03.23,0:02:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Două surori care au fost trimise împreună,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.96,0:02:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,au lucrat împreună și s-au \Nîntors împreună ca eroi.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.79,0:02:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serios? Asta chiar e ceva.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:11.67,0:02:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Numele surorii mai mari \Neste Tsuranari Hakua.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.58,0:02:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iar sora mai mică este Kougyoku.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.87,0:02:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci de care mă voi ocupa eu?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.43,0:02:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sora mai mare? Sau cea mai mică?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:23.61,0:02:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amândouă.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.87,0:02:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amândouă?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.78,0:02:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.67,0:02:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Din moment ce e un caz așa de rar, am hotărât ca amândouă să tranziteze împreună la o viață obișnuită.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.07,0:02:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iar tu, Uro, te vei ocupa de \Naceastă misiune periculoasă.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.10,0:02:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Decizia a fost unanimă.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.81,0:02:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superiorii chiar cred că pot să-mi dea orice misiune doresc ei?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu poți refuza și nici nu te poți scoate.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.32,0:02:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi-ar plăcea să primesc niște scuze din când în când.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:52.57,0:02:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ceea ce înseamnă,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.94,0:02:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,de acum, amândouă veți trăi aici pe Pământ ca niște cetățeni obișnuiți.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.67,0:02:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aveți vreo întrebare?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă avem vreo întrebare, auzi la el.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.70,0:03:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mai întâi, trebuie să faci o plecăciune, om de rând!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.13,0:03:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E o lipsă totală de respesc să ne vorbește de parcă am fi la același rang.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.08,0:03:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am mai spus asta, dar nu mai sunteți eroine, ci niște persoane obișnuite.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.57,0:03:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De acum înainte, va trebui să învățați și să munciți ca restul oamenilor.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.09,0:03:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Să-i spui unui cavaler că este o „persoană obșinuită” este foarte enervant.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.60,0:03:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă eu sunt o persoană obișnuită, atunci tu ce ești? Un vierme?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sau poate un gunoi?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.78,0:03:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu mă voi schimba!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.25,0:03:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sfidătoare ca întotdeauna.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.09,0:03:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine, copii ca tine se adaptează repede la viața de zi cu zi.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, sigur.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.10,0:03:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-o crezi tu că voi trăi \Nprintre oamenii de rând.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-i așa, surioară?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.43,0:03:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cu sabia, armura și \Nornamentele pe care le-am făcut,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,sora mea va fi mereu un erou...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu se va schimba niciodată.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.51,0:03:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt sigură de asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-am întors!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.74,0:04:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vai, am avut atât de multe de făcut la muncă! Dar am dat {\i1}tot{\i0} ce am putut!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.37,0:04:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uro, pregătește cina!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Felicitări.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Văd că ai tot lucrat full-time în ultimele zile.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.47,0:04:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to build up experience \Nquickly so I can level up my skills!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.44,0:04:19.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't keep being a bother to the shop manager forever.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.27,0:04:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How admirable of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.36,0:04:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with me there, the atmosphere of the shop has improved, so I can rise quickly.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.27,0:04:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.97,0:04:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there is something I want.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.23,0:04:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should be able to get it \Nif I save up just a little more.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.55,0:04:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't work yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just an ordinary person now—
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm tired of hearing that!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.38,0:04:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of time. They say it's good to keep a goal in mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.73,0:04:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sister of mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want to hear my talk?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.52,0:04:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's your pride as a hero?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you getting so upset about?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.48,0:05:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not as though I can avoid\N rubbing shoulders with the masses,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't mean\N I have given up my pride.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.32,0:05:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the way home from work at the café, \NI got a little cake so cutesy you'd squeal!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.56,0:05:13.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't understand... what are you saying?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's with that ordinary outfit?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the silver armor I gave you?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.77,0:05:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, I'd feel out of place wearing that!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try being fashionable?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.47,0:05:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's tons of cute clothing in this world.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.81,0:05:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kougyoku, you should join us next time we—
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.56,0:05:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the sword? \NThe sword I gave you!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Don't you know?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.59,0:05:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The earth has this legal system.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.45,0:05:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll arrest you if you\N have a blade over 6 cm long.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A law?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.21,0:05:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And gems?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the ruby in which I instilled divine protection?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I wore that it would get stolen!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.44,0:05:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be dangerous.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't get shot, so don't worry!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And anyway, there's no \Nsuch thing as demons in this world,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.95,0:06:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I don't need divine protection.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:03.04,0:06:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not my sister anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kougyoku.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.56,0:06:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.69,0:06:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take off that eyepatch.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.79,0:06:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you can actually see.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably dangerous to \Nnot have depth perception.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.45,0:06:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.45,0:06:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up with that attitude?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uro, hurry up and make dinner.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.00,0:06:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the floor's sopping wet! Wipe that up!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to eat dinner?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.04,0:06:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't like ginger roast?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.53,0:06:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you making a weapon?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.54,0:07:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.57,0:07:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's what you've \Nbeen doing your whole life.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.10,0:07:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The days keep coming, and you keep working in your studio,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,making weapons and \Narmor and protective ornaments.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All for Hakua.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wasn't it hard for you?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.96,0:07:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That no matter how much work you put into the weapons,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.84,0:07:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the only one who received the honor and praise was the hero Hakua?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.82,0:07:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though you're the \None who gave Hakua her power,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no one paid any attention to you.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.10,0:07:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just keep giving, but you can't get anything in return.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.79,0:07:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the fate of a supporting character.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.61,0:07:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the crowds speak of Hakua,\N my swords and armor are included.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.29,0:07:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is my pride.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.22,0:07:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't need any reward.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.77,0:08:00.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's exactly why it's so hard \Nfor me to forgive Hakua for changing.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tossing away the things\N I've made so carefully,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for some "part-time job", for some "fashion"!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.47,0:08:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you changing my Hakua?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.22,0:08:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamada Uro!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my job.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.53,0:08:19.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like you made Hakua into a hero,\N I'll make you two into regular citizens.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't change!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of that I am sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.68,0:08:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'll show you, \Nand make Hakua a hero again!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.07,0:08:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that sword's all bent.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.08,0:08:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's proof you're not looking at what's in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't make a weapon that way.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.83,0:08:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike the world you want to be in, \Nyou can't easily use magic here.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.27,0:08:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to become a craftsperson in this world, it'd be best to start from scratch—
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I use it that way, it's a weapon.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.53,0:08:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:51.68,0:08:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh... huh.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.69,0:09:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsuranari Kougyoku. Former craftsperson.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.56,0:09:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Item-maker who used all of her\N power for her older sister, a hero.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.59,0:09:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like she's still trapped in a dream.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.45,0:09:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that dream is probably...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.39,0:09:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking so gloomy?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.00,0:09:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't forgive the world that takes\N the sister that she gave her all to,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:25.56,0:09:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and turns her into something mediocre, isn't she just the model younger sister?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh, how innocent...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.29,0:09:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having dreams is an admirable thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.89,0:09:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'd like if she'd stop having her dreams depend on another person.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.59,0:09:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she's entrusting her \Nentire worth as a person to her sister...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a fool.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think we should try to arrange a little get-together?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get-together?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.18,0:10:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Assemble Alice and the heroes you've worked with so far at the beach,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.72,0:10:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and let Kougyoku-chan meet \Nsomeone other than Hakua-san.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.59,0:10:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can count on me to be there to help.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty good idea,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.03,0:10:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you're not just asking because \Nyou want to see girls in swimsuits, are you?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.18,0:10:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I refuse to confirm or deny my motivations.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.72,0:10:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\t(2500,4440,\c&H110E0E&\3c&H040910&)}Don't try and hide your fetishes.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.35,0:10:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll relax on the beach in the afternoon, and have barbecue for dinner.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.39,0:10:37.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, with full stomachs,\N we'll have fun with fireworks.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a good chance for you to get to know each other better.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.54,0:10:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hakua, Kyogyoku, say hello.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.50,0:10:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aye.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I thought this was a pain,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.66,0:10:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but as long as I'm here I plan to have fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:51.59,0:10:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you all.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you too, say hello.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:59.72,0:11:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, I bet it'll be a lot of fun!\N I can't wait to eat some barbecue!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.04,0:11:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Karon-san's as energetic as ever!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.43,0:11:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But to be sure, this is a great chance for us to\N meet new people and strengthen our relationships.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:12.65,0:11:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think? Airo-san.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:15.13,0:11:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I have to say one way or the other, this feels like a bother to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:19.23,0:11:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate the heat.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:20.74,0:11:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little one, remember to \Nplay nice with your friends.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:24.48,0:11:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since when have you been my mother, Alice?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:27.98,0:11:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\t(4000,5420,\c&H110E0E&\3c&H040910&)}Oh my. You don’t have to call me your mother, "young lady" will do fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:34.69,0:11:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:35.90,0:11:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Killer technique,\N Ultra No-Way-In-Hell Super Spike!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:44.45,0:11:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With an exceedingly lame attack name like that, there's no way you could defeat me, Karon!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means, it's my turn!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:53.75,0:11:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miracle Hyper Jump-Powered Smash!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, I did it!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:01.60,0:12:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think I couldn't stop it at this range...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Working part-time all night might be hard,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:05.40,0:12:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I haven't felt this kind of indignity since I was a hero!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How irritating!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:11.21,0:12:14.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Working part-time all night sure is hard.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you're tired, \Nyou can't summon any strength.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:16.94,0:12:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However. That physical \Nlimitation is a good thing!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Striving to reach new heights,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:23.87,0:12:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,dealing with a body that refuses to do as it's told...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:27.57,0:12:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, your will may be broken harder than your body in the end, but even so!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:31.69,0:12:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Buckling down and refusing to give in
Dialogue: 100,0:12:33.55,0:12:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,creates its own kind of \Nlight at the end of the tunnel!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things aren't going to go as you expect.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:40.62,0:12:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's because you can't reach\N those heights that life is interesting!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:52.65,0:12:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first glance, you seemed dim-witted,\N and your speech appeared foolishly blunt,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you say can some rather deep things.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:59.43,0:13:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if you start looking up to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:01.97,0:13:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I may be impertinent \Nand arrogant, but I like you.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:05.46,0:13:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that we're friends, why don't we run off into the sunset together?!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:09.02,0:13:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's midday as hell right now, but I concur!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:17.64,0:13:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did they learn that kind of meat-headed communication?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:22.50,0:13:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, just looking at them is sweltering.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:25.50,0:13:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, my, isn't it a good thing?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:28.03,0:13:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blending bodies and heat, \Ntheir hearts move as one.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kind of communication is lovely!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:33.88,0:13:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-If you say so...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:35.46,0:13:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Of course, I also love the quiet bonding we are sharing right now.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:41.12,0:13:43.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are many ways of \Ninteracting with other people.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:44.08,0:13:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, there are so\N many people in this world!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:48.22,0:13:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reca-san, you have such a big heart.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.44,0:13:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As one would expect of a former princess.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:53.55,0:13:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are times where I can't quite say the same about myself
Dialogue: 100,0:13:57.72,0:14:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know it's not good, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:00.99,0:14:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:01.81,0:14:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are the decorations all Rococo?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:04.36,0:14:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't we decide on a Gothic style?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:07.07,0:14:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because I like swirly things!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Airo-san, you're too picky about your scenery!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:13.57,0:14:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh—what's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:16.03,0:14:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This kind of thing works out best when you stick to the plan!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:20.48,0:14:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, my, if you get that upset about it,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:23.74,0:14:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you're just as bad as Karon-san!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely mistaken!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell Uro-kun about this!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:32.54,0:14:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:36.57,0:14:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:45.97,0:14:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beautiful former heroes\N in swimsuits! And the ocean!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this paradise?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:52.32,0:14:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a peaceful scene!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:55.53,0:14:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, peaceful.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apart from you being here.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:03.87,0:15:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She can't fit in with them, huh.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:06.14,0:15:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl... she reminds me a lot of how you were long ago.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:09.79,0:15:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, she's just like you.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:11.87,0:15:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:13.61,0:15:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Compared to Uro-san, \NKougyoku-chan is way, way cuter!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four-eyes, you're getting on my nerves.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:20.23,0:15:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want things that are important to you to remain important.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you can't accept new things.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You become obstinate and close in on yourself.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:28.58,0:15:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just like you!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say she's like me, but you shouldn't treat her that way.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know that.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't tease her.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:37.48,0:15:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe just a little.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It does make me want to... stir things up.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.77,0:15:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything tastes better \Nwhen you eat outside!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uro, more alcohol.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're drinking too much.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:11.87,0:16:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kougyoku-san!\NPerfectly-done meat, just for you!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:19.21,0:16:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I've been aiming to talk to you since this afternoon,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I became too caught\N up frolicking with Hakua-san.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:27.86,0:16:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kougyoku-san, let's be friends too!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:32.27,0:16:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woah, rejected! I just got hit with a clear, outright rejection!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:36.06,0:16:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, it was your own fault.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:38.31,0:16:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, heroes sure have such bad manners, it's a problem.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Woah, from the witch too!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let this loud one be,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:46.15,0:16:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and let's relax and talk over there, just us two support characters.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a pain too.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oi, Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:59.85,0:17:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it already! You've \Ngot to try to communicate or—
Dialogue: 100,0:17:03.52,0:17:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:04.94,0:17:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "friends"?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "communication"?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:08.28,0:17:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you get along with them?!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a hero, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:13.89,0:17:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What have you been so \Nunhappy about this whole time?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's going out of their way to have fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:18.70,0:17:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! It's because of that that you're—
Dialogue: 100,0:17:31.67,0:17:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what\N my younger sister is thinking.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:37.75,0:17:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to check on her.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:39.94,0:17:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unde ești?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:46.91,0:17:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.46,0:17:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously, where could she have gone?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:51.34,0:17:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alice went after her, so I'm sure it's nothing too extreme, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is something to \Nbe worried about, isn't it.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:58.04,0:18:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's bound to be up to something,
Dialogue: 100,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that old monster.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:02.94,0:18:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She does tend to play \Nsome nasty tricks sometimes.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:07.19,0:18:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's overloaded with cuteness.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.77,0:18:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei, Uro.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:12.42,0:18:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sper că nu este supărată pe noi Kougyoku.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:15.65,0:18:16.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Airo?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:17.27,0:18:20.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kind of understand her feelings.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:20.31,0:18:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As support characters, no matter how hard we try, we can't get the glory.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:25.25,0:18:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we get so\N picky about certain things.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:28.76,0:18:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's really important to her is probably...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:31.80,0:18:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. She won't be mad.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:34.68,0:18:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Hakua understands that too.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:42.20,0:18:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where could Kougyoku-san be—
Dialogue: 100,0:18:57.62,0:18:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:59.22,0:19:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What could she possibly be \Ntalking about, that sister of mine?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:02.42,0:19:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All my plans have gone down the drain!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hakua!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finished a new gem!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's full of protection!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:20.71,0:19:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as you have this, you're invincible!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:31.04,0:19:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief, she's so troublesome!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:34.36,0:19:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:37.40,0:19:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Încă nu am reușit s-o găsim...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:39.13,0:19:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And where did that meat-head go?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:41.64,0:19:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And four-eyes, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:44.25,0:19:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Karon-san's gone too, then that means...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it is Alice.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Airo-san?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:55.52,0:19:58.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad! Reca! Stay close to me!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:06.83,0:20:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alice! Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're there!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:20.91,0:20:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We have the heroes. If you want them back, come to the beach!"
Dialogue: 100,0:20:43.78,0:20:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamada Uro!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:45.15,0:20:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Send Hakua and me back to our world!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.94,0:20:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alice. What's this about?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:50.82,0:20:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just helping out a woman\N with something to say.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:53.92,0:20:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here to test you, anytime, anywhere.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:58.74,0:21:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose I could get you to \Nstop putting my life on Hard Mode?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:02.06,0:21:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Send us back immediately!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:09.99,0:21:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kougyoku. You made that \Ncrossbow by yourself, didn't you.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:13.44,0:21:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't shoot with that.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not held together well, and it's crooked.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:17.39,0:21:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but as long as \Nyou can't accept this world,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:20.01,0:21:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can't craft anything.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:22.32,0:21:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taci!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cu ce drept spui asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:24.51,0:21:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crafting things in this \Nworld is a very difficult thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:29.31,0:21:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as you're not looking\N properly at the things in front of you,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:31.83,0:21:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can't make anything.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:36.16,0:21:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:37.91,0:21:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you get in my way?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:40.26,0:21:43.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just love the hero Hakua,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:43.17,0:21:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to make things for her
Dialogue: 100,0:21:45.35,0:21:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so she can be praised,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:50.30,0:21:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and free, and strong... that's all.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:01.86,0:22:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You stupid little sister!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:05.31,0:22:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Become the greatest craftsperson in this world, \Ntoo! This time, without any magic!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:10.29,0:22:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kougyoku!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:12.24,0:22:13.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hakua...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:14.10,0:22:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was planning for a situation \Nwhere you were more excited,
Dialogue: 100,0:22:18.04,0:22:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that's not a big deal anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:20.40,0:22:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here. It's a present for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:24.04,0:22:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:25.96,0:22:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hakua's been working so hard at her part-time job to buy this for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:30.10,0:22:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Day in and day out, living a life she couldn't get used to...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:33.76,0:22:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I can do anything if I put my mind to it.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:38.26,0:22:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:39.79,0:22:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why would you do something like that for me?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:42.20,0:22:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a supporting character.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:44.20,0:22:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my job to give you—
Dialogue: 100,0:22:46.55,0:22:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you being so\N picky about? Sister of mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:50.66,0:22:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I received so much from \Nyou back in the other world.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:53.77,0:22:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time it's my turn to give.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:56.77,0:22:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earn money through dealing with people.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:59.28,0:23:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}I'll take on the daily tasks of a hero.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:02.35,0:23:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way you can put your whole \Nheart into mastering craftsmanship.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:07.20,0:23:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that means you—
Dialogue: 100,0:23:08.69,0:23:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 100,0:23:11.54,0:23:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the other world \NI was one of the greatest hero.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:14.52,0:23:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in this world...
Dialogue: 100,0:23:19.95,0:23:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm your only sister.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:31.14,0:23:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And—
Dialogue: 100,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woah!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:34.50,0:23:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you ought to be a little fashionable too.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:37.90,0:23:41.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like me, you can't \Nlet your beauty go to waste.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:49.99,0:23:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surioară...
Dialogue: 100,0:23:51.98,0:23:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surioară!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:56.05,0:23:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surioară...
Dialogue: 100,0:23:58.47,0:23:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surioară...
Dialogue: 100,0:24:12.62,0:24:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a sparkler!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:14.54,0:24:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:15.84,0:24:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, wait your turn!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:17.14,0:24:19.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl's just like you after all.
Dialogue: 100,0:24:19.76,0:24:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You keep saying that, but in what way?
Dialogue: 100,0:24:21.44,0:24:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever she decides something's important, she won't let go no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 100,0:24:25.70,0:24:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, very stubborn.
Dialogue: 100,0:24:27.55,0:24:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, when you put it that way, I kind of—
Dialogue: 100,0:24:30.30,0:24:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Karon! Don't wave the\N sparkler around! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:34.37,0:24:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody let me down...
Dialogue: 100,0:24:37.26,0:24:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that matter settled, it's so much fun to fireworks with everyone!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:42.40,0:24:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were easily captured \Npretty early on, weren't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:24:46.02,0:24:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure are the kind of witch that little kids worry about.
Dialogue: 100,0:24:49.76,0:24:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce ai spus?
Dialogue: 100,0:24:50.69,0:24:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haide să mai aprindem una!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:51.71,0:24:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hei, așteaptă!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:55.08,0:24:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, am pierdut din nou!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:57.69,0:24:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ura, șapte la rând!
Dialogue: 100,0:24:59.76,0:25:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asta e surioara mea!
Dialogue: 100,0:25:02.94,0:25:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu o voi pierde pe următoarea!
Dialogue: 100,0:25:04.64,0:25:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tot eu voi câștiga!
Dialogue: 100,0:25:05.98,0:25:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și voi face opt puncte!
Dialogue: 100,0:25:07.45,0:25:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce briză plăcută.
Dialogue: 100,0:25:50.29,0:25:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu credeți că există și lucruri \Nfrumoase în această lume?
Dialogue: 100,0:26:04.64,0:26:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ba da!
